{"title":"🔧TypeScript入门配置","uid":"b729b46ac2965294edc575cf8c0e9868","slug":"how-to-learn-typescript/typescript入门配置","date":"2020-01-08T16:30:20.000Z","updated":"2021-07-10T11:44:11.729Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/how-to-learn-typescript/typescript入门配置.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"Your-Environment\"><a href=\"#Your-Environment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Your Environment\"></a>Your Environment</h2><p><strong>你需要做的准备：</strong></p>\n<p>💡  Node.js &gt; 8.0，最好是最新的稳定版<br>💡  一个包管理工具 npm 或者 yarn<br>💡  一个文本编辑器或者 IDE</p>\n<br>\n\n<h2 id=\"Install-TypeScript\"><a href=\"#Install-TypeScript\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install TypeScript\"></a>Install TypeScript</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install TypeScript -g</code></pre>\n<p>安装好后，看看版本信息</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tsc -v</code></pre>\n\n<br>\n\n<h2 id=\"Init-Project\"><a href=\"#Init-Project\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Init Project\"></a>Init Project</h2><p>先创建下目录</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir ts-study &amp;&amp; cd ts-study</code></pre>\n\n<p>再创建 src 目录（一般用来存放项目代码）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir src &amp;&amp; touch src&#x2F;index.ts</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> 如果你的系统是Windows的话，<code>touch</code>并不会生效，你可以用<code>New-Item</code>来代替<code>touch</code>，<a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/issues/8621\">查看相关issue</a></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">New-Alias touch New-Item</code></pre>\n\n<p>初始化项目 package.json</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm init</code></pre>\n\n<p>初始化 ts 配置文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tsc --init</code></pre>\n\n<br>\n\n<h2 id=\"VSCode-Auto-Compile\"><a href=\"#VSCode-Auto-Compile\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VSCode Auto Compile\"></a>VSCode Auto Compile</h2><p>在终端下拉菜单中选择运行任务</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/TypeScript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/ts-1.png?x-oss-process=style/2333\"></p>\n<p>选择 <code>tsc:监视</code> （当你的文件发生改动时会自动编译）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/TypeScript%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/ts-2.png?x-oss-process=style/2333\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Your Environment你需要做的准备： 💡 Node.js &gt; 8.0，最好是最新的稳定版💡 一个包管理工具 npm 或者 yarn💡 一个文本编辑器或者 IDE Install TypeScriptnpm install TypeScript -g 安装好后，看...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":499,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"TypeScript","slug":"TypeScript","count":1,"path":"api/categories/TypeScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"TypeScript Basic","slug":"TypeScript-Basic","count":1,"path":"api/tags/TypeScript-Basic.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Your-Environment\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Your Environment</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Install-TypeScript\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Install TypeScript</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Init-Project\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Init Project</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#VSCode-Auto-Compile\"><span class=\"toc-text\">VSCode Auto Compile</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"大鹏","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/avator/567.png","link":"/","description":"Web Developer","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/KongValley","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"ico